OL,5,G0210 Ramsay's Hotel Hell
OL,6,     FThe Monticello Hotel: Gordon
OL,7,     Fvisits the struggling Monticello
OL,8,     FHotel in Longview, Washington. Can
OL,9,     Fhe keep the doors to this
OL,10,     F90-year-old establishment open and
OL,11,     Fsave 50 jobs?
OL,12,G0300 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe competition kicks off at North
OL,14,     FBridge Street B&B in Hawick, where
OL,15,     FEileen Walsh and Emanuel Forte's
OL,16,     Fpurple-themed rooms cause quite a
OL,17,     Freaction among their guests.
