OL,5,G0325 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt The Golden Fleece in Cumbria,
OL,7,     FSylvia Spark and Robert Cowan aim
OL,8,     Fto please with some local fare at
OL,9,     Fbreakfast. But the plates swim in
OL,10,     Fgrease and the eggs are hard.
OL,11,G0350 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FThe third visit is to The Bubble
OL,13,     FInn in Stenson, Derbyshire, where
OL,14,     Fformer semi-pro boxer Connie
OL,15,     FEleftheriou thinks he can knock
OL,16,     Fout the competition... until some
OL,17,     Funsightly stains are found.
