OL,5,G0420 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FMelinda Beckett-Hughes hosts the
OL,7,     Ffinal visit, at Ayuda House in
OL,8,     FGreater Manchester. Her guests
OL,9,     Fexpect perfection but are shocked
OL,10,     Fto find a dirty towel and dust
OL,11,     Fgalore.
OL,12,G0445 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIt's the final day and the B&Bers
OL,14,     Fmeet for the last time to settle
OL,15,     Fsome scores. There's some
OL,16,     Fdisastrous breakfast and
OL,17,     Fcleanliness feedback, which makes
OL,18,     Ffor tough decisions.
